
Features:
	- info.plist manipulation
		- Add/remove user-configured searches
	- Add via URL (auto-discovery)
		- Get URL of frontmost browser

Commands:

	Config:
		- Browse engines & variants in Alfred
			- Add user searches
		- Browse user searches
			- Remove user searches

